2010/1/23 Ken <kstanley@...>
>
> Colin, I was curious, does the HyperNEAT that you've implemented include any demo experiments?
>

The released test harness/gui is currently set up to run XOR, and
there's Binary-6-Multiplexer in there also. As it stands the test
harness wires together the various bits of code required to get up and
running, whereas in SharpNEAT 1 that is done inside of classes that
implement IExperiment, instances of which can be 'plugged in' in a
more straightforward manner.
